data.description: Beautifully updated NE facing duet in desirable Danbury Park with no direct rear neighbors! With vaulted ceilings, this home is open and spacious with an abundance of natural light. Hardwood-style floors and plantation shutters throughout provide added elegance. The eat-in kitchen features white cabinets, granite countertops, recessed lighting and walk-out to the private back patio. The spacious primary suite has an updated bathroom with dual vanity, skylight & large walk-in closet. The secondary bedrooms share a convenient balcony patio to enjoy. Other conveniences include an interior laundry area, no direct rear neighbors & 2-car garage. Located steps away from Orloff Park, an 8-acre green space with kids' play areas, basketball courts, picnic tables, walking trails & lots of open space to run and play. Close proximity to top schools, the shops and restaurants of quaint downtown Pleasanton, 580/680 hwys & Bart transportation. Completely turn-key with low HOA fees! Open Sunday 1-4pm
